
  if (+):
      condition

    Start a 'if...[elif]...[else]...fi' block and test if specified condition 
    holds.
    'condition' is a mathematical expression, whose evaluation is interpreted 
    as { 0=false | other=true }.

    Example:
      [#1] image.jpg if ia<64 add 50% elif ia<128 add 25% elif ia<192 sub 25% 
       else sub 50% fi cut 0,255

    Tutorial: https://gmic.eu/tutorial/iffi

